thread.title: Cynthia Humphreys

author: Cynthia Humphreys
title: Cynthia Humphreys
text: After an exhausting search for a reliable supplier of USB cards with artwork relating to tax work, I finally came upon CustomUSB.com. After initial midday e-mail contact with Elliot Portnoy, I received a mock-up and Quote: within a couple of hours; we sealed the deal the same day. Within days I received our order, beautifully and securely packed. The product is just what we hoped for and the service is first class. We are pleased!! I highly recommend this supplier.
